# Organization / moderation

Between 2017 and 2019 I ran several pytest/tox [sprints](https://wiki.python.org/moin/EuroPython2017/Sprints) and [help desks](https://ep2018.europython.eu/conference/p/oliver-bestwalter) at EuroPython.

Moderated some discussions and panels at PythonCamps (German): 

* Entwickeln, Testen und Verteilen mit SaltStack und Vagrant (oder Docker?) -> [session info](https://barcamptools.eu/pycamp201403/sessions)
* tox + conda -> [session info / notes](https://barcamptools.eu/pycamp201804/events/37163d8f-6122-4d7c-9d07-aa3d87ef00b3/tox_conda)
* Maintainer Burnout -> [session info / notes](https://barcamptools.eu/pycamp201704/events/37163d8f-6122-4d7c-9d07-aa3d87ef00b3/maintainer_burnout)
